; Exported by cyclic fixed-tip tracking script
; Smooth motion-only program: capture markers are ignored, so the tracked sweep does not stop for images.
G90
G1 B0.0 F50
G4 P2000     ; pause/dwell for 2000 ms
G1 B-2.3 F50
G4 P2000     ; pause/dwell for 2000 ms
G1 B0.0 F50
G4 P2000     ; pause/dwell for 2000 ms
G1 B-4.3F50
G4 P2000     ; pause/dwell for 2000 ms
G1 B0.0 F50

